    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's exactly how it feels. like i've been running a race that has no finish line, just... nothingness on the other side. it feels like everyone keeps telling me \"it gets better\" or \"you're so strong,\" but they don't get it. there's nothing left to be strong for. does it really just... make sense to just stop?",
